{{Youmay|the ancient, dead language of an alien species|the [[Vodran (species)/Legends|species]] or their [[Vodran/Legends|native planet]]}}
{{Conjecture|legends}}
'''Vodran''' was the native language of the [[Vodran (species)/Legends|Vodran]] species from [[Vodran/Legends|Vodran]].

However, after the [[Third Battle of Vontor]] (c. [[25,100 BBY]]), Vodrans increasingly replaced Vodran language with [[Huttese/Legends|Huttese]], the language of their [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] masters. As of [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]], the Vodran language was extinct, with no known speakers in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology">''[[Ultimate Alien Anthology]]''</ref>

